Package: nvim-cmp
Architecture: all
Depends:
 ${misc:Depends},
 ${vim-addon:Depends},
 neovim,
 nvim-snippy,
Description: A completion plugin for neovim coded in Lua
 This package also includes several sources:
   * cmp-buffer   - source for buffer words
   * cmp-cmdline  - source for vim's cmdline
   * nvim-cmp-lsp - source for neovim LSP client
   * cmp-path     - source for path
   * cmp-snippy   - source for nvim-snippy
